    {
      "id": "1ad4750c-f3ba-8048-9ab5-e43bb4336ffc",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The work uses Multimodal Learning Analytics to gain insights into how students with special needs respond to behavior analysis therapy. The ML models used achieve outstanding performances when it comes to predicting behavioral change. Moreover, the authors discuss how the multi-modal nature of the data improves model performance relative to the usual educational-only data.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1ad4750c-f3ba-8048-9ab5-e43bb4336ffc",
        "parent": {
